embeds.description:
You know those rules you agreed to when you decided to make your discord account?

-: This includes DM advertising; i.e. sending a server invite without asking permission first.

→ https://discord.com/guidelines

embeds.title: [2] Hate Speech
embeds.description: Any direct/indirect form of discrimination/racism/hate speech is strictly prohibited here.

embeds.title: [3] NSFW Content
embeds.description: No nsfw content will be tolerated anywhere in this server. This includes nsfw emojis. No posting/talking about gore or graphic images.

embeds.title: [4] Advertising
embeds.description: Advertising servers is strictly prohibited in all channels of The Ville, including your trade ads.

embeds.title: [5] Mini Modding
embeds.description:
We appreciate it, but ping the Moderators for any urgent issues in chat. 
All other questions or concerns can be handled by contacting staff at support .
Mini-modding is basically an user acting as a mod in the absence of an actual moderator.

embeds.title: [6] Scamming
embeds.description: Scamming over any bot is strictly prohibited and will result in an immediate ban.

embeds.title: [7] Spam
embeds.description: You know what spam is, and so do we. No clipboard posting/copy paste/spam typing.

embeds.title: [8] Names
embeds.description: Nicknames must be SFW and mentionable.

embeds.title: [9] Religion/Politics
embeds.description: Any extensive conversations surrounding religion or politics are not allowed

embeds.title: [10]  Phishing
